  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Administrative Assistant (Underwriting Commercial Lines)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide customer service to clients on the general enquiries pertaining to clients’ policies;</li>\n  <li>Create and modify client/agent codes and updating of clients’ information in the system;</li>\n  <li>Process and issue policies /endorsements;</li>\n  <li>Check all policies and endorsements processed;</li>\n  <li>Prepare cover letters to attach to policies for dispatch to clients;</li>\n  <li>Prepare draft policy clauses and endorsements;</li>\n  <li>Responsible for ensuring the accuracy of renewal notices, claims statistics and summary of insurance for review;</li>\n  <li>Sort renewal notices and extract policy files for renewals due, prepare claims statistics and summary of insurance;</li>\n  <li>Support the maintenance of an effective policy and/or document filing system by ensuring the proper filing endorsement copies faxed by clients are being filed together with office copy;</li>\n  <li>Ensure policy jacket’s accuracy and sufficient stocks are in place;</li>\n  <li>Other duties and assignments that may be instructed by the superior from time to time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma holders or related discipline;</li>\n  <li>Preferably with minimum 1 year working experience;</li>\n  <li>Prepare to take up Certificate In General Insurance (CGI) exam if required;</li>\n  <li>Willingness to learn and meticulous;</li>\n  <li>Possess good interpersonal and communications skills;</li>\n  <li>An attractive remuneration and bonus package will be offered to the successful candidate.</li>\n</ul>",
